author: akarasulu
msg: Started defining interfaces for an LDAP URL datatype and its parser.
Implementations of the parser will need to leverage the existing name
parser within the ldapd.common.name package generated by antlr.  Basically
the components of the URL will be parsed by different parsers and the
implementor will only need to be concerned with RFC 2255 and RFC 1738
